properties.name: Jared Golden
properties.biography: Jared Golden is the Democratic representative from Maine's 2nd Congressional District in the U.S. House. Golden was elected to the office on November 6, 2018. Golden is a former Democratic member of the Maine House of Representatives, representing District 60 from 2014 to 2018.
